### Submit Block

Sits below all four horizon accordions at the bottom of the Vision State tab.

**Version Name Field**  
Label: Name This Version  
Helper text: Give this version of your Clarity Compass a name — or use the one we've suggested.  
Type: Text input  
Default value: Auto-generated recommendation based on current date — format: "Clarity Compass — [Month Year]" (e.g., "Clarity Compass — February 2026")  
